---
title: Free Episodes | Elixir Sips
---

%p Here are all of the free episodes so far.  For the rest, just sign up below.

= partial 'partials/subscribe_button'

.episodes-list
  - free_episodes.each do |episode|
    .episode-list-item
      %a{ href: episode.url }
        %h5= episode.title_with_subscriber_tag
        .episode-list-item-screenshot
          = image_tag(episode.small_cover_image_url, class: "cover-image", width: 300, height: 169)
          - if episode.free?
            = image_tag('play_small.png', class: 'play')
        %p= episode.synopsis
